in the scope of \f(CW\*(C`use English\*(C'\fR.  For that reason, saying \f(CW\*(C`use
English\*(C'\fR in libraries is strongly discouraged.  See the
Devel::SawAmpersand module documentation from \s-1CPAN\s0
